ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 194, New Brunswick
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 194 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK, with respect to the RAINSTORM, that affected the province, from September 29, 2015 to October 1, 2015.
